      "separateLinks": true,
      "visible": true,
      "id": "summary",
      "content": "<p><strong>CTO and Technical Lead with over 12 years of experience</strong>, whose professional journey demonstrates a strong <strong>propensity for innovation and continuous learning</strong>. Starting from a solid foundation as a Full Stack Developer, <strong>I have developed expertise in software architecture and engineering</strong>, mastering design patterns in both frontend and backend.</p><p>This attitude toward change is demonstrated by the <strong>recent adoption of emerging technologies</strong>: I have led the <strong>development of AI agents</strong> for automation, and realized personal projects in the <strong>Web3 space</strong>, such as wallets and smart accounts. I combine technical leadership and architectural vision with the ability to rapidly assimilate and apply new paradigms.</p>"
    },
