          "summary": "<p>Activities included <strong>software architecture definition</strong> and <strong>direction of technological choices</strong> at the enterprise level, ensuring full alignment with business objectives. Responsibilities covered the management of <strong>complex multi-tenant systems</strong>, solving fundamental challenges such as <strong>scalability</strong> and implementation of <strong>robust Access Control Lists (ACLs)</strong>. Supervised the <strong>direction and coordination</strong> of development teams, optimizing operational workflows. Implemented <strong>advanced and secure authentication systems</strong> and developed <strong>AI agents</strong>. The supporting infrastructure utilized containerization with <strong>Docker</strong> and <strong>scalable AWS services</strong> to ensure performance and resilience.</p>",
          "url": {
